sequenceDiagram
    participant External as external_user_server
    participant Sync as sync-user-data
    participant DB as clavis-db
    participant OPA as opa
    participant Redis

    Note over Sync: Periodic synchronization job

    Sync->>External: Fetch updated users
    External-->>Sync: User data

    Sync->>Sync: Transform to normalized JSON
    Sync->>Sync: Compute checksum

    Sync->>DB: Retrieve stored checksum
    DB-->>Sync: Existing checksum

    alt Data changed
        Sync->>DB: Upsert user record

        Sync->>Redis: Delete keys matching pattern opa:{userId}:*

        Sync->>OPA: Compute user permissions
        OPA-->>Sync: Computed rights

        Sync->>Redis: Store computed rights (key: opa:{userId}:{scriptId})
    else No change
        Note over Sync: Skip recomputation
    end